  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Accommodation summary</strong></p>
<p><strong>Ground floor</strong></p>
<p>The shared sauna, ski and boot room and Esprit Snow Club room are location on the ground floor.</p>
<p><strong>Third floor</strong></p>
<p>The chalet entrance, dining area, living room with fireplace and stairs to Room Three are located on the third floor. Once you go up the internal stairs from the lounge, Room Three is a quad room with a double bed and bunk beds.                                                 </p>
<p><strong>Fourth floor</strong></p>
<p>The fourth floor has Suite 1 &amp; 2 - both rooms have a double and twin bedroom, plus a bathroom. The children's snug area is at the top of the stairs.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Room description</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Room 3 sleeps four. Quad room with double and twin bunks in two inter connecting sleeping areas with shower and WC.</li>
<li><span>Suite 1 sleeps four. Twin room and double room with balcony, separated by central bath, shower, WC room and short open passage way.</span></li>
<li><span>Suite 2 sleeps 4. Twin room and double room with balcony, separated by central bath, shower, WC room and short open passage way.</span></li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
